snippet.title: Rise of Elements - Official Trailer | WLG Showcase 2025
snippet.description: Rise of Elements is a Match-3 style narrative puzzle game with classic RPG elements, where players will clash for victory. Compete in Argos’s Tournament of Champions to achieve elemental mastery and rid the world of Aetheron of the Void’s looming threat. Check out the Rise of Elements trailer to see Match-3 gameplay and more.
